      "description": "Shot Tracer ® • Live Tracer • 3D Map Tracer • Putt Reader • Golf Video Editor • AR Golf Graphics • Live Scoring\n\nTrace your golf shots like on TV and turn every swing into stunning golf content.\n\nShot Tracer® is the ultimate golf tracer, golf ball flight tracker, golf video editor, and augmented reality golf app trusted by golfers worldwide and voted Best Golf App by Golf Digest and Golf Magazine.\n\nCreate broadcast-style golf videos, analyze your game, improve your putting, and relive your rounds on over 44,000 golf courses worldwide directly on your iPhone and iPad.\n\nSHOT TRACER ® LIVE TRACER\n\nCreate TV-style golf ball tracers with advanced tracking technology.\n\n• NEW Live Tracer for real-time ball tracing while recording\n• Auto distance measurement of golf shots\n• Distances to pin overlays\n• Dynamic tracer graphics and customization\n• Works on any golf course no special hardware required no internet required\n\n3D MAP TRACER & COURSE FLYOVERS\n\nRelive your shots from a stunning bird’s-eye perspective.\n\n• Create 3D flyovers on 44,000+ golf courses worldwide\n• Create cinematic hole previews and shot replays\n• Showcase strategy, landing zones, and shot placement\n• Professional aerial-style golf visualizations\n\nGOLF VIDEO EDITOR\n\nCreate professional golf videos directly on your iPhone and iPad with automatic ball flight tracking.\n\n• NEW Broadcast-style scoreboards and hole information graphics\n• Video-in-video overlays with animations\n• Auto captions and voice overlays\n• Add custom text, logos, images, and graphics\n• Alpha channel export support for advanced editing workflows\n• Full customization of all graphics and layouts\n• Sound effects library\n• Voice-over and captions\n• Custom image overlay\n• Custom text overlay\n• Faster rendering and export performance\n\nPROFESSIONAL SCORECARD EDITOR\n\nCreate stunning animated golf scorecards in seconds.\n\n• Built-in database with 44,000+ golf course scorecards worldwide\n• Dozens of animated professional scorecard templates\n• Fully customizable scorecard animations and graphics\n\nLIVE SCORING FROM ALL MAJOR TOURS\n\n• Live scoring support from major professional golf tours\n\nAR GREEN READING & PUTT READER\n\nBring broadcast-proofed green reading technology to your game.\n\n• Augmented reality green reading\n• Visual putt lines and slope analysis\n• Understand break, speed, and aiming point\n• Improve putting confidence and green reading skills\n\nAR FUN TRACER MODE\n\nCreate engaging augmented reality golf content.\n\n• Hit targets, hoops, and AR challenges\n• Shoot down UFOs and moving targets\n• Create fun golf clips for social media\n\nMORE FEATURES\n\n• Live golf scores from major tours\n• Golf GPS and distance tools\n• Digital scorecards and scoreboard editor\n• 44,000+ golf course database\n• Works on iPhone and iPad\n• Continuous weekly feature updates and improvements\n\nCreated by golfers for golfers.\n\nShot Tracer® is a registered trademark of Visual Vertigo Software Technologies GmbH, registered with the USPTO and international trademark offices. All rights reserved.\n\nTerms of use: https://www.apple.com/legal/internet-services/itunes/dev/stdeula/",
